    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255120/extras/80cb34cd93e44e762a28d09874d52fe2.poster.avif?t=1743517584\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255120/extras/80cb34cd93e44e762a28d09874d52fe2.webm?t=1743517584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255120/extras/80cb34cd93e44e762a28d09874d52fe2.mp4?t=1743517584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet The Hoverpelago</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine several themed islands to be able to do the perfect hoversurf, play with gravity and speed to be the best.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels Are Never The Same</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With procedural level generation whenever a game is started, everyone together will have new challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet New Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Miner crew has grown, with new characters to choose from and have fun with.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Global Leaderboards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to be the best in the world by reaching the highest height.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun Together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real Physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural Levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adrenaline Speed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cool Toon Shader.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day to night transition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Radical Movements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kids love this game.</p></li></ul>",
